description: A super detached Victorian property on one of the greatest places.

This house has been designed and build to an impeccable standard offering luxurious and elegant living. The accommodation is arranged over four floors comprising a large entrance hall, living room with tall sash windows, dining room, study and WC on the ground floor.
This family house is very well designed by a famous designer.
This fantastic family home is designed for a 8 persons or more and specialy for kids who like swimming cause there is a swimming pool.
